            },
            {          
                "margin": [0, 10, 0, 0],
                "style":"pdfContent",
                "preserveLeadingSpaces": true,
                "text": "              Now. therefore, take notice under section 11(f) of the Chandigarh Rural Inhabitation (Area within Red Line of Revenue Estates. Abadi Area) Construction and Reconstruction Building Bye Laws for villages (both within and outside Municipal Limits) falling in Union Territory of Chandigarh. 2017. for villages in the Municipal area of Municipal Corporation to elect or re-erect the building as these are not according to the sanctioned plan! without getting the plan sanctioned from Municipal Corporation. Chandigarh. As per rules. the above violations mentioned in the table are required to be demolished by dated. In case you wish to rebut the notice, you are provided with an opportunity to appear before the undersigned on _______________________ at____________ to submit your reply."
            },
            {          
                "margin": [0, 10, 0, 0],
                "style":"pdfContent",
                "preserveLeadingSpaces": true,
                "text": "              It may please be noted that in case you fail to appear before the undersigned on the date mentioned above, the undersigned shall be constrained to presume that the notice as given. hold good and the structure raised in contravention of rules shall be ordered to be removed at your expense without giving any further notice."            
            },
